original: Janson, Einar Henrik, disponent, Norrahammar, f. 20/12/95 i Gbg av kassör Ludvig J. o. Anna Dahlqvist. G. 1. m. Amalia Sofia Fabricius-Hansen; 2. m. Agneta Fjaestad. Barn: Rolf-Einar f. 23, Jarl-Helge 25, Bo 33. — Stud. v. CTI, hand:inst., Techn. i Al-te nbur g. Ing. v. Bililerudsi A-B, Jös-sefor-s Bruk, 18-22, driftsing. v. Amotsfors Pappersbruk 23-31, tekn. led. där 31-38, driftsled. o. tekn. chef v. Thorsviks A-B i Norrahammar 38, disp. där 39’.
translated: Janson, Einar Henrik, manager, Norrahammar, b. 20/12/95 in Gothenburg to cashier Ludvig J. and Anna Dahlqvist. Married 1st to Amalia Sofia Fabricius-Hansen in 19xx; 2nd to Agneta Fjaestad. Children: Rolf-Einar b. 23, Jarl-Helge b. 25, Bo b. 33. Studied at CTI, School of Commerce, Technological Institute in Altenburg. Engineer at Bililerudsi A-B and Jössefors Bruk from 1918 to 1922, technical director and engineering manager at Amotsfors Pappersbruk from 1923 to 1931, technical director and manager at Thorsviks A-B in Norrahammar in 1938, and manager since 1939.
